@template core/email_html

Template for all html emails. Note that it may wrap content formatted
elsewhere in another a module template.

Context variables required for this template:
* sitefullname
* siteshortname
* sitewwwroot
* subject
* to
* toname
* touserid
* tousername
* from
* fromname
* replyto
* replytoname
* body
* prefix

Example context (json):
{
"prefix": "[Prefix Text]",
"body": "Email body"
}
}}

